Class Maximum

java.lang.Object
com.telenav.kivakit.core.value.count.Count
com.telenav.kivakit.core.value.count.Maximum
All Implemented Interfaces:
Countable, Sized, DoubleQuantizable, Maximizable<Count>, Minimizable<Count>, Quantizable, Stringable, StringSource, Serializable, Comparable<Count>
public class Maximum extends Count
A count value that is an maximum. This class mainly exists to clarify APIs by giving a meaning to the count value.

jonathanl (shibo)
